Package survey

Class Summary
Answer Creates options for an Answer to a question for tests
FileSystem Creates a file system to save the Surveys/Tests
MainUI Main UI Class for console use of the Survey System
Question Question class for methods and options available to all question types
RankingMatching New type of question that emulates ranking and matching questions in a survey/test
SAEssay New type of question that emulates Short Answer and Essay questions in a survey/test
Survey Survey Object that contains list of questions and controls the system
TrueFalseMC New type of question that emulates True/False and Multiple choice questions in a survey/test
 

Enum Summary
AnswerType enum for use when decipering Answer types for the UI
QuestionType enum for question types for ease of use in switch statements
